            "text_content_4": "Nova-Creative not only has exquisite designs, their customer support is outstanding too! They helped me tweak my template to get it exactly the way I imagined it in my head. You will not regret doing business with them. The entire experience is just incredible! Thanks again!!",
            "img_author_4": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tes-4.jpg",
