            "info_name_4": "Customer",
            "info_trade_4": "From Envato",
            "item_5": true,
            "text_content_5": "This theme has an incredible amount of features to begin with, and the support team was even more impressive. I reached out regarding minor changes, and the team was fast and extremely helpful in solving my problems. I highly recommend this theme and any other themes from this team!",
            "img_author_5": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/tes-9.jpg",
